OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779801070
OL,3,CHollywood star Channing Tatum starts
OL,4,Cfilming new movie at Isle of Man TT
OL,6,FHollywood royalty Channing Tatum has
OL,7,Fbeen spotted at the Isle of Man TT
OL,8,Fraces, filming scenes for a new movie.
OL,10,FThe star of Step Up and 21 Jump Street
OL,11,Fwas wearing leathers as the cameras
OL,12,Fcaptured scenes for the film, titled
OL,13,F'Isle of Man'.
OL,15,FFellow Hollywood superstar Brad Pitt
OL,16,Fis a producer on the movie - the first
OL,17,Ftime Hollywood has featured the TT.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
