CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779801070
OL,3,CHollywood star Channing Tatum starts
OL,4,Cfilming new movie at Isle of Man TT
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Granada earlier in
OL,7,FMay, Morecambe-based TT hero John
OL,8,FMcGuinness said: "I speak to Channing
OL,9,Fa little bit and have a little bit of
OL,10,Fa chat with him, and he just loves it
OL,11,F- loves the bikes - I think it's
OL,12,Ffantastic.
OL,14,F"It's a big production It's a big
OL,15,FHollywood thing. I know some of the
OL,16,Fguys who are involved in it and, you
OL,17,Fknow, let's hope it's a success."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779801070
OL,3,CHollywood star Channing Tatum starts
OL,4,Cfilming new movie at Isle of Man TT
OL,6,FSpeaking about the film last month,
OL,7,FPaul Phillips, Head of Motorsport,
OL,8,FDepartment for Enterprise, said: "The
OL,9,FTT has an extraordinary story to tell,
OL,10,Fand what makes this so authentic is
OL,11,Fthat filming begins at the event
OL,12,Fitself - capturing the real
OL,13,Fenvironment, with the real atmosphere,
OL,14,Fand against the backdrop of the Isle
OL,15,Fof Man.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779801070
OL,3,CHollywood star Channing Tatum starts
OL,4,Cfilming new movie at Isle of Man TT
OL,6,F"The reach of a project like this goes
OL,7,Ffar beyond motorsport. It creates a
OL,8,Fnew opportunity for the Isle of Man
OL,9,Fand a chance to connect the TT, and
OL,10,Fthe place that makes it possible, with
OL,11,Fentirely new audiences around the
OL,12,Fworld."
OL,14,FSarah Maltby MHK, Political Member
OL,15,Fwith responsibility for Motorsport and
OL,16,FTourism, added: "This is a major
OL,17,Fmoment not only for the Isle of Man TT
OL,18,FRaces, but for the Isle of Man as a
OL,19,Fwhole.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779801070
OL,3,CHollywood star Channing Tatum starts
OL,4,Cfilming new movie at Isle of Man TT
OL,6,F"To have filming begin at this year's
OL,7,Fevent is another step forward in
OL,8,Ftaking the TT story to a global
OL,9,Faudience, and with it, showcasing the
OL,10,FIsland itself to millions of people
OL,11,Faround the world.
OL,13,F"The TT has always been one of the
OL,14,FIsle of Man's greatest assets, a world-
OL,15,Fclass event with a unique identity and
OL,16,Finternational appeal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
