PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779801070
OL,3,CHollywood star Channing Tatum starts
OL,4,Cfilming new movie at Isle of Man TT
OL,6,F"Projects of this scale have the
OL,7,Fpotential to create lasting value,
OL,8,Fsupporting destination awareness,
OL,9,Fstrengthening our global profile, and
OL,10,Fhelping more people discover what
OL,11,Fmakes the Isle of Man so special."
OL,13,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
